_header: I am Mayus that is both young and sheen
_description: English couplets on illustrations of the months of the year

BLHar5401.First Lines:
I am Mayus þat is bothe gay & sheneffull of swete flowers
                    rede whyte & grene…
BLHar5401.Last Lines:
…I am Decembre most of plenteAnd kynge of riches & of
                    rialte
BLHar5401.Note: Folio number reflects the most recent foliation.
